{
  "stem": "7414.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are going to-- to die under my knife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have to tell her a story, yes?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I told her, look, the father of the child, I don't know where he is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taken by the Germans somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have to work to earn a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she told me, look, I am not going to touch you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she gave me an offer, a very decent offer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She told me, I am going to take you to my clinic, and you will stay with me till the child will be born.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we will decide what we are going to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She did not-- she did not know that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She-- probably she did not suspect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She did not think, perhaps, about-- she saw it as a doctor thing, yes?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She wanted to help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course, I did not take her offer up because I went back home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my sister, I-- I think that she will die when she heard that this is nothing to do about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the least of our worries because two days later, my brother-in-law comes home very agitated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told us that a student of his recognize him on the street and started to blackmail him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a Jew, as a police officer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A-- you-- that was two things enough to hang him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he started to blackmail him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he knew that it is time to move somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he went to his headquarters, and he told them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- apparently he did not tell them that he is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't know if they knew or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, they found for him a place in Warsaw for him and his family.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
